// to select a word
double click the word

// to select a sentence 
press and hold ctrl and click on any word in the sentence

// to select multiple consecutive sentences 
first press and hold ctrl and click on any word in the first sentence, 
then release the ctrl key and press shift key and hold, and click on the senteces

// to select a portion of a sentence or a paragraph
first click where you want the selection starts ( cursor flashing ), 
then press and hold shit key and click where you want the selection ends. 

